description:
This is a 28 minute workout called '27 MIN Orange Theory Inspired Treadmill Workout!' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Today we are doing a tough 27 MIN Orange Theory Inspired Tread Workout. If you have never been to an Orange Theory class, we highly recommend it! The treadmill section is usually half the class with the other half being rowing/floor exercises. Let us know how you like it!

Thanks to PopSugar for posting this workout: https://www.popsugar.com/fitness/Orangetheory-Treadmill-Workout-45523405

27:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
IBX Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/
